    <item>
      <title>RED DA Compliance (Part 2): Espressif’s Platform Support, Templates, and Pathways for Conformity</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/2025/07/esp32-red-da-en18031-compliance-guide-part2/</link>
